		"description": "<p>At 18th level, the celestial blood in your veins has fully asserted itself. You gain the following abilities:</p>\n<h2>Heaven&rsquo;s Ire</h2>\n<p>Once per long rest you may cast the spell @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.1ueqga5yu55bntti]{Fire Storm}. Intelligence is your spellcasting modifier for this spell.</p>\n<h2>Mighty Wings</h2>\n<p>Your fly speed granted by your @UUID[Compendium.a5e-bloody-heretics.bloody-heretics.Item.gWUTY3pRWMWEt6rR]{Angelic Aspect} increases to 60 feet. Additionally, your spectral wings persist until you dismiss them as a bonus action.</p>\n<h2>Truthseeker</h2>\n<p>You automatically detect when a creature is lying.</p>",
